,"kind":"text"},{"text":"VariantRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? = nil)","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If the action is expecting a parameter, then the correct type of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parameter must be given as "},{"code":"parameter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":".  If the action is expecting no"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parameters then "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"parameter"},{"text":" must be ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"type":"text","text":".  See"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.ActionGroup.get_action_parameter_type"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If the [type","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] implementation supports asynchronous remote"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"activation over D-Bus, this call may return before the relevant","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"D-Bus traffic has been sent, or any replies have been received. In","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"order to block on such asynchronous activation calls,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.DBusConnection.flush"},{"type":"text","text":"] should be called prior to the code, which"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"depends on the result of the action activation. Without flushing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the D-Bus connection, there is no guarantee that the action would"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"have been activated.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The following code which runs in a remote app instance, shows an","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"example of a ‘quit’ action being activated on the primary app","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instance over D-Bus. Here [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.DBusConnection.flush"},{"type":"text","text":"] is called"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"before ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"exit()"},{"text":". Without ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_dbus_connection_flush()"},{"type":"text","text":", the ‘quit’ action"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"may fail to be activated on the primary instance."}]},{"code":["\/\/ call ‘quit’ action on primary instance","g_action_group_activate_action (G_ACTION_GROUP (app), \"quit\", NULL);","","\/\/ make sure the action is activated now","g_dbus_connection_flush (…);","","g_debug (\"Application has been terminated. Exiting.\");","","exit (0);"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"c"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroupRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroupRef\/ActionGroupProtocol-Implementations"]]},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ActionGroupRef/activateAction(actionName:parameter:)":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/actiongroupref\/activateaction(actionname:parameter:)","title":"activateAction(actionName:parameter:)","abstract":[{"text":"Activate the named action within ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"actionGroup"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroupRef\/activateAction(actionName:parameter:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"activateAction","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"actio